data.title: Professional athletes Chris Evert, tennis player at left, and Miami Dolphins quarterback Bob Griese, right, with a representative from S&H Green Stamps: Fort Lauderdale, Florida
data.meta_description: Local call number: PR21476 Title: [Professional athletes Chris Evert, tennis player at left, and Miami Dolphins quarterback Bob Griese, right, with a representative from S&H Green Stamps: Fort Lauderdale, Florida] Personal Author: Erickson, Roy. Date: Photographed on January 5, 1973. Physical descrip: 1 photoprint: b&w; 8 x 10 in. Series Title: (Print Collections. N2006-13, Roy Erickson collection.) General note: Chris Evert was born in Fort Lauderdale and graduated from the St. Thomas Aquinas High School. General note: Bob Griese was quarterback from 1967-1979, playing for the team during their perfect undefeated season in 1972. General note: The photographer, Roy Erickson, was a professional photographer in the Ft. Lauderdale area and was affiliated with the Best of Broward magazine for over 10 years.
